ed. Finally, drawing on the lessons learnt from the campaign, the report ends by presenting some final recommendations to the European Union (part 3).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Opening-Doors-for-Europes-Children-Lessons-and-Recommendations.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Embed of Opening-Doors-for-Europes-Children-Lessons-and-Recommendations.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-3b0f2933-124e-4c70-9248-2d207aea836b\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Opening-Doors-for-Europes-Children-Lessons-and-Recommendations.pdf\">Opening-Doors-for-Europes-Children-Lessons-and-Recommendations<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Opening-Doors-for-Europes-Children-Lessons-and-Recommendations.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-3b0f2933-124e-4c70-9248-2d207aea836b\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This final report reflects on progress towards child protection system reform across campaign countries as  well as developments at the EU level.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3785,"template":"","tags":[67,25,40,51,81,82,80],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Report: Opening Doors for Europe\u2019s Children - Hope and Homes<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Read the final report on progress towards child protection system reform across European countries and developments at EU level\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/publications\/opening-doors-for-europes-children\/\" \/>\